======================================================

COPY COMPNENT WILL WORK ONLY TO COPY FILES FROM LOCAL EC2-INSTANCE TO INSIDE OF A CONTAINER
ADD COMPNENT WILL WORK ONLY TO GET THE FILES FROM INTERNET

